Mantle's smile widened as he shook Prowl's hand. They had thought, well all 
of them but Cinder, that Striker and his team were gone, yet at least Prowl 
had survived. They had worried the most about him, for the same reason as 
the one that caused Cinder's face to be redder than her natural coloring 
right now, though Prowl didn't seem to notice.

"We're all ok. Someone told us that you're the only one of Striker's team 
left on the planet?" Mantle's statement was a question, because he wasn't 
sure. He had other friends on Striker's team, and he hoped that they wern't 
all gone.
